name: Richie's Plank Experience
summary:
The viral VR plank game played by millions!
Discover why everyone is walking the plank, including PewDiePie, CardiB, Fulham FC, Joe Rogan, K-Pop stars - BTS and more!

Test your fear of heights in Richie’s Plank Experience, designed to invoke the strongest possible emotions in the shortest possible time. Entertain your friends and family as they walk the plank 80 stories high and experience terrifying real fear, knees weak and palms sweaty!
